verbose_text: As a result, we identified a novel [myosin, heavy chain 7, cardiac muscle, beta (MYH7), p.Asn885Thr] mutation, a variant of uncertain significance [troponin T type 2 (cardiac) (TNNT2), p.Arg296His] and a double heterozygous [protein kinase, AMP activated, gamma 2 non catalytic subunit (PRKAG2), p.Gly100Ser plus MYH7, p.Arg719Trp] mutation.
